      • collapseApproximate

        public static final LogRecordHandler collapseApproximate
        Collapse records in a heuristic way to make reading easier. This is particularly relevant to branches which go to a physical console, or a file which you'd like to keep small.

      • collapseExact

        public static final LogRecordHandler collapseExact
